#

Honey Mustard Glazed Chicken Thighs

$15.99
480 kcal

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

Comfort FoodFamily-FriendlyEasy Dinner

Description

Juicy chicken thighs glazed with a sweet and tangy honey mustard sauce, paired with roasted seasonal vegetables.

Ingredients

  • Chicken thighs: 4 pieces
  • Honey: 1/4 cup
  • Dijon mustard: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic cloves: 3, minced
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Mixed seasonal vegetables (carrots, broccoli, bell peppers): 2 cups
  • Fresh thyme: 1 tablespoon
